title: 820-01700 NO BOOT WITH BATTERY
message:
hello,
please i have one macbook mainboard 820-01700
client have replace battery and laptop no start
i have check and the problem is when i connect cable between the battery and the mainboard for info batt
when i remove, macbook start perfectly
When i put cable laptop stay 0.110A and no power
I have test with other battery, other cable and same problem
Thanks for your help

title: 820-01700 NO BOOT WITH BATTERY
message:
Check voltage and diode mode to ground on SCL/SDA battery lines; U6950 is suspect.
Be sure R5220/21 are both OK.

title: 820-01700 NO BOOT WITH BATTERY
message:
U6950 is beautiful
R5220/21 are good : 4.7 Omh
line SCL 0.500
Line SDA : 0.500

title: 820-01700 NO BOOT WITH BATTERY
message:
for be sure, i have replace U6950 and all works fine!!
Thanks a lot
